{
  "texts": [
    "However, no FQ resistance SNPs were found in either phased assembly in sample A.",
    "Using MLST, the phased 1 assembly could be identified as belonging to the ST10 sequence type.",
    "Interestingly, some FQ resistant E. coli isolates obtained from four farms, including A and B, were also typed as ST10 by MLST (Ringenier et al., under review).",
    "In contrast, no sequence type could be determined for the phased 2 assembly.",
    "For the E. coli MAG in sample B, three phased assemblies were generated with varying coverages and CheckM quality measures."
  ]
}